OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781632101
OL,3,CCare home manager fined after two
OL,4,Cwheelchair users drowned on day trip
OL,6,FA Devon care home manager has been
OL,7,Fordered to pay #4,000 after two people
OL,8,Fin wheelchairs drowned when their boat
OL,9,Fcapsized on a day out.
OL,11,FJanice Sowden, 60, previously pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty to failing to provide safe care
OL,13,Fand treatment that resulted in
OL,14,Favoidable harm to Alexander Wood,
OL,15,FAlison Tilsley and Kate Dart.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
