OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781632101
OL,3,CCare home manager fined after two
OL,4,Cwheelchair users drowned on day trip
OL,6,FMr Wood, who was 43 and had four
OL,7,Fchildren, and Ms Tilsley, 63, died
OL,8,Fwhen the wheelyboat they were in
OL,9,Fcapsized at Roadford Lake Activity
OL,10,FCentre, with their heavy wheelchairs
OL,11,Fdragging them under the water.
OL,13,FMs Dart also suffered serious injury
OL,14,Fin the incident, during which Sowden,
OL,15,Fas the registered manager, was
OL,16,Fresponsible for health and safety.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781632101
OL,3,CCare home manager fined after two
OL,4,Cwheelchair users drowned on day trip
OL,6,FExeter Magistrates' Court heard Sowden
OL,7,Ffailed to assess the risks of the
OL,8,Fouting in June 2022, which involved
OL,9,Ftaking six people, all of whom were
OL,10,Fwheelchair users, from Burdon Grange
OL,11,FCare Home to the activity centre.
OL,13,FJames Marsland, prosecuting, said : "A
OL,14,Fwheelyboat, ie, a boat designed to
OL,15,Fcarry wheelchair users, had been hired
OL,16,Ffrom the centre for a trip on the lake.
OL,18,F"Alexander Wood and Alison Tilsley, in
OL,19,Fparticular, were strapped into
OL,20,Felectric wheelchairs without any means
OL,21,Fof being released from them."
OL,26,@uD@eOUzD@AOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781632101
OL,3,CCare home manager fined after two
OL,4,Cwheelchair users drowned on day trip
OL,6,FThe court heard the vessel started to
OL,7,Ftake on water within minutes and soon
OL,8,Fcapsized.
OL,10,FMr Marsland said Mr Wood and Ms
OL,11,FTilsley were "drowned by the weight of
OL,12,Ftheir wheelchairs" as they pulled them
OL,13,Funder the water.
OL,15,FHe said: "Miss Sowden did not
OL,16,Fundertake any risk assessment in
OL,17,Frelation to the needs of the service
OL,18,Fusers... Nor did she ensure that any
OL,19,Fsuch risk assessment did take place.
OL,26,@sD@NOUtD@RO]wD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781632101
OL,3,CCare home manager fined after two
OL,4,Cwheelchair users drowned on day trip
OL,6,F"This is a classic case of serious
OL,7,Fnegligence."
OL,9,FSowden, of Beaworthy, Devon, had been
OL,10,Fappointed registered manager at the
OL,11,Fhome in 2016 and was described as
OL,12,Fhaving previously been "caring" and
OL,13,F"diligent" in her work.
OL,15,FHowever, the court heard a "cultural
OL,16,Fcomplacency" developed in the home in
OL,17,Fthe run-up to the incident and
OL,18,Fstandards had slipped.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@LO]tD@XOUtD@_O]uD@AOUuD@JO]wD@
OL,26,A\OUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781632101
OL,3,CCare home manager fined after two
OL,4,Cwheelchair users drowned on day trip
OL,6,FJudge Stuart Smith said the facility
OL,7,Fhad been home to "extremely
OL,8,Fvulnerable" service users and it
OL,9,Fshould have been obvious to Sowden
OL,10,Fthat health and safety assessments
OL,11,Fneeded to be completed before the trip.
OL,13,FHe added that insufficient
OL,14,Fconsideration was also given to the
OL,15,Fcapabilities of staff members, one of
OL,16,Fwhom could not swim, and described
OL,17,FSowden as "blase" about risk.
OL,26,@oD@ROUpD@KO]yD@KOUyD@PrryD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781632101
OL,3,CCare home manager fined after two
OL,4,Cwheelchair users drowned on day trip
OL,6,FThe court heard Sowden went on to
OL,7,Fattempt to fabricate evidence of
OL,8,Fhealth and safety considerations
OL,9,Ffollowing the incident, creating a
OL,10,Ffake checklist for the boat trip to
OL,11,F"deceive" investigators.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, Sowden was ordered to pay
OL,14,Fa total of #4,090, including a #190
OL,15,Fgovernment surcharge and #2,000 as a
OL,16,Fcontribution to prosecution costs.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781632101
OL,3,CCare home manager fined after two
OL,4,Cwheelchair users drowned on day trip
OL,6,FThe court heard Sowden, who has
OL,7,Fmobility issues, currently receives
OL,8,Fbenefits and will likely have to
OL,9,Fretrain in order to find work again,
OL,10,Foutside of the care sector.
OL,12,FAddressing Sowden, Judge Smith said:
OL,13,F"This case is nothing short of
OL,14,Fdevastating... The lives of two much-
OL,15,Floved residents, Alexander Wood and
OL,16,FAlison Tilsley, have been lost.
OL,18,F"This was in no small part a direct
OL,19,Fconsequence of your cavalier attitude
OL,20,Fto good health and safety practice.
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
