CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781632101
OL,3,CCare home manager fined after two
OL,4,Cwheelchair users drowned on day trip
OL,6,F"This incident has caused immeasurable
OL,7,Fgrief to the families of Alex and
OL,8,FAlison."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@HO]
